---
import MiFoto from "../../assets/img/vishal.png";
---

<div
  class="mx-auto mt-16 flex max-w-6xl flex-col items-center gap-12 px-6 lg:flex-row"
>
  <!-- Interactive Profile Picture Container -->
  <div class="relative w-full max-w-[280px] sm:max-w-[340px] flex-shrink-0 group">
    <!-- Glow border -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-cyan-500 rounded-3xl blur-[12px] opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
    
    <div class="relative bg-gray-900 border border-white/10 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl aspect-square shadow-2xl">
      <img
        src={MiFoto.src}
        alt="Vishal Rawal"
        class="h-full w-full object-cover group-hover:scale-102 transition-transform duration-500"
      />
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Content Biography Details -->
  <div class="flex-1 text-center lg:text-left space-y-6">
    <div class="space-y-2">
      <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-cyan-400 uppercase">Biography</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white font-display">
        I am <span class="text-gradient">Vishal Rawal</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm sm:text-base font-medium leading-relaxed">
      A passionate Fullstack Web Developer specialized in crafting high-fidelity user experiences and reliable backend architectures. I continuously strive to solve complex challenges by writing clean, modular, and performant code.
    </p>

    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm sm:text-base font-medium leading-relaxed">
      My background involves extensive practicing in modern Javascript technologies, including React, Angular, Vue, and Tailwind CSS. On the backend, I design socket connections, databases, and express routes to create comprehensive real-time systems.
    </p>

    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm sm:text-base font-medium leading-relaxed">
      I believe in open-source collaboration and the constant evolution of my skill set. My ultimate career focus is to architect large-scale client applications, leverage MERN integrations, and contribute to cutting-edge web developments.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>